___                 &kp C_PREV          &kp C_VOL_DN        &kp C_VOL_UP        &kp C_NEXT          &mmv MOVE_LEFT      &mmv MOVE_DOWN      &mmv MOVE_UP        &mmv MOVE_RIGHT     &mkp MB4
___                 &kp C_PP            &kp C_BRI_DN        &kp C_BRI_UP        &kp C_MUTE          &msc SCRL_RIGHT     &msc SCRL_UP        &msc SCRL_DOWN      &msc SCRL_LEFT      &mkp MCLK
